{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-awesome-readme-js","path":"/schlessera/awesome-wp-cli/readme","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Track Awesome List"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"b28a18f8-ef23-5f37-ada7-65ccb403dc69","html":"<!--lint ignore double-link--><html><head></head><body>\n<h1 id=\"awesome-wp-cli-awesome-awesome-lint-img-srchttpsgithubcomschlesseraawesome-wp-clirawmasterassetswp-cli-bw-trans-filled-tight311x160png-altwp-cli-logo-alignright-height80\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#awesome-wp-cli-awesome-awesome-lint-img-srchttpsgithubcomschlesseraawesome-wp-clirawmasterassetswp-cli-bw-trans-filled-tight311x160png-altwp-cli-logo-alignright-height80\" aria-label=\"awesome wp cli awesome awesome lint img srchttpsgithubcomschlesseraawesome wp clirawmasterassetswp cli bw trans filled tight311x160png altwp cli logo alignright height80 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Awesome WP-CLI <a href=\"https://awesome.re\"><img src=\"https://awesome.re/badge.svg\" alt=\"Awesome\"></a> <a href=\"https://github.com/schlessera/awesome-wp-cli/actions?query=workflow%3Aawesome-lint\"><img src=\"https://github.com/schlessera/awesome-wp-cli/workflows/awesome-lint/badge.svg\" alt=\"awesome-lint\"></a> <a href=\"https://wp-cli.org/\"><img src=\"https://github.com/schlessera/awesome-wp-cli/raw/master/assets/wp-cli-bw-trans-filled-tight@311x160.png\" alt=\"WP-CLI Logo\" align=\"right\" height=\"80\"></a></h1>\n<!--lint ignore double-link--><html><head></head><body>\n<p><a href=\"https://wp-cli.org/\">WP-CLI</a> is the command-line interface for WordPress. It offers a complete alternative to the WordPress admin dashboard, often even surpassing its functionality or enabling new use cases. It also comes with a rich ecosystem of third-party commands that are bundled in Composer packages or directly integrated into WordPresss plugins or themes.</p>\n<h2 id=\"contents\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#contents\" aria-label=\"contents permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Contents</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#official-links\">Official links</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#third-party-packages\">Third-party packages</a>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#package-discovery\">Package discovery</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#notable-packages\">Notable packages</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"#tutorials--guides\">Tutorials &#x26; guides</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"official-links\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#official-links\" aria-label=\"official links permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Official links</h2>\n<p>Everything relevant that is directly part of the official WP-CLI team.</p>\n<!--lint ignore double-link--><html><head></head><body>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wp-cli.org/\">wp-cli.org</a> - Homepage of the WP-CLI project.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/cli/handbook/\">WP-CLI handbook</a> - Guides on how to use or extend WP-CLI.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://developer.wordpress.org/cli/commands/\">WP-CLI command reference</a> - Reference documentation for all the official WP-CLI commands.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/cli/\">Make WordPress.org - CLI</a> - Main entry point for contributing to WP-CLI.\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/cli/handbook/contributing/\">Contributing guide</a> - Everything you need to know to contribute to the tool or its infrastructure.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/chat/\">Official MakeWP Slack</a> - Official Slack team where all international contributions to WordPress and its teams are discussed.\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://wordpress.slack.com/messages/cli/\">#cli channel</a> - The official support channel for WP-CLI and the WordPress CLI team.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/cli/good-first-issues/\">Good first issues</a> - List of issues on that are limited in scope and complexity.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/wp-cli\">WP-CLI GitHub organization</a> - Canonical home of the WP-CLI source code.\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/wp-cli/wp-cli\">WP-CLI framework repository</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/wp-cli/wp-cli\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">4.6k</span></span></a> - The source code for the WP-CLI framework that powers all of the commands.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/wp-cli/wp-cli-bundle\">WP-CLI bundle repository</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/wp-cli/wp-cli-bundle\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">65</span></span></a> - The source for the WP-CLI \"binary\" and how it is assembled.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/wp-cli/wp-cli-tests\">WP-CLI tests repository</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/wp-cli/wp-cli-tests\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">22</span></span></a> - The testing framework used throughout all WP-CLI repositories.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"third-party-packages\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#third-party-packages\" aria-label=\"third party packages permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Third-party packages</h2>\n<p>Unofficial third-party packages.</p>\n<h3 id=\"package-discovery\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#package-discovery\" aria-label=\"package discovery permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Package discovery</h3>\n<p>Ways of searching for third-party packages you can use.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://packagist.org/?type=wp-cli-package\">Packagist.org search by WP-CLI package type</a> - Composer packages filtered by type <code class=\"language-text\">wp-cli-package</code>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/search?q=WP_CLI%3A%3Aadd_command%28+NOT+Akismet_CLI+NOT+elementor+NOT+WordCamp_CLI_Miscellaneous+NOT+W3TotalCache_Command+extension%3Aphp+language%3APHP+-org%3Awp-cli+-path%3Avendor+-path%3Awp-content+-path%3Apublic+-path%3Adeployer+-path%3Aweb+-path%3Asrc%2Fvendor+-path%3Aapp+-path%3Awordpress+-filename%3Aentity-command.php+-filename%3Aclass-wc-cli.php+-filename%3Awp-cli-bp.php+fork%3Afalse+-filename%3Aextension-command.php+-filename%3Acron-command.php+-filename%3Awp-seo-main.php+-path%3Aplugins+-path%3Adata+-path%3Abackup+-path%3Ademo+-path%3Awordcamp.org+-path%3Awordpress.org+-filename%3Alanguage-command.php+-filename%3Aredirection-cli.php+-path%3Athemes+-path%3Alibrary+-filename%3Aeval-command+-filename%3Arole-command+-filename%3Awidget-command+-filename%3Acache-command.php+-path%3Awp-app+-path%3Apublic_html+-filename%3Aqueue.php+-path%3AmyWeb+-path%3Adocroot+-path%3Awebsite&#x26;type=Code\">GitHub.com search for WP-CLI integrations</a> - Heavily pre-filtered search for repositories that use <code class=\"language-text\">WP_CLI::add_command()</code>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"notable-packages\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#notable-packages\" aria-label=\"notable packages permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Notable packages</h3>\n<p>Third-party packages that are commonly useful.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/Yoast/wp-cli-faker\">Yoast/wp-cli-faker</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/Yoast/wp-cli-faker\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">48</span></span></a> - Generate fake WordPress and WooCommerce content for testing purposes.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/aaemnnosttv/wp-cli-login-command\">aaemnnosttv/wp-cli-login-command</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/aaemnnosttv/wp-cli-login-command\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">254</span></span></a> - Login to WordPress with secure passwordless magic links.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/schlessera/wp-cli-psysh\">schlessera/wp-cli-psysh</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/schlessera/wp-cli-psysh\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">19</span></span></a> - Replace WP-CLI shell standard REPL with <a href=\"http://psysh.org/\">PsySH</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/php-stubs/wp-cli-stubs\">php-stubs/wp-cli-stubs</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/php-stubs/wp-cli-stubs\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">12</span></span></a> - WP-CLI function and class declaration stubs for static analysis.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"tutorials--guides\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#tutorials--guides\" aria-label=\"tutorials  guides permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Tutorials &#x26; guides</h2>\n<p>Websites, ebooks, PDFs, talks and slide shows about how to make the most out of WP-CLI.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://pascalbirchler.com/an-introduction-to-wp-cli/\">An Introduction to WP-CLI</a> - Introductory article that introduces the main concepts and some popular use cases of WP-CLI.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.tv/2017/05/22/alain-schlesser-controlling-wordpress-through-the-command-line-introduction-to-wp-cli/\">Controlling WordPress through the Command Line</a> - Introductory talk that covers the very basics of the command line for people who never used the console before.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://guides.wp-bullet.com/category/wp-cli/\">WP Bullet WP-CLI Guides</a> - Snippet-based guides that solve specific use cases.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DlxbRYpZdQg\">Siteground Webinar: Learn How WP-CLI Can Make Your Life Easier</a> - Practical examples on how you can improve your workflows with WP-CLI.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"contribute\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#contribute\" aria-label=\"contribute permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Contribute</h2>\n<p>Contributions welcome! Read the <a href=\"https://github.com/schlessera/awesome-wp-cli/blob/master/contributing.md\">contribution guidelines</a> first.</p>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#awesome-wp-cli-awesome-awesome-lint-img-srchttpsgithubcomschlesseraawesome-wp-clirawmasterassetswp-cli-bw-trans-filled-tight311x160png-altwp-cli-logo-alignright-height80\">Awesome WP-CLI <img src=\"https://awesome.re/badge.svg\" alt=\"Awesome\"> <img src=\"https://github.com/schlessera/awesome-wp-cli/workflows/awesome-lint/badge.svg\" alt=\"awesome-lint\"> <img src=\"https://github.com/schlessera/awesome-wp-cli/raw/master/assets/wp-cli-bw-trans-filled-tight@311x160.png\" alt=\"WP-CLI Logo\" align=\"right\" height=\"80\"></a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#contents\">Contents</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#official-links\">Official links</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#third-party-packages\">Third-party packages</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#package-discovery\">Package discovery</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#notable-packages\">Notable packages</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#tutorials--guides\">Tutorials &#x26; guides</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#contribute\">Contribute</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","headings":[{"id":"awesome-wp-cli-awesome-awesome-lint-img-srchttpsgithubcomschlesseraawesome-wp-clirawmasterassetswp-cli-bw-trans-filled-tight311x160png-altwp-cli-logo-alignright-height80","value":"Awesome WP-CLI Awesome awesome-lint <img src=\"https://git